'''Rytal Prime''' was the capital city of the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] [[Dayark]]. It held the moon's main spaceport. Rytal Prime was also the location of the [[Kathol Republic senatorial chambers]].

In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Corvette/Legends|corvette]] ''[[FarStar]]'' was ordered to land at the spaceport after surrendering to the [[Kathol Republic Navy]].

